metadata.name: Master the mind
metadata.description:
The dark Side is the dark side within us that arises as a result of our unwillingness to accept and hate the impulses from the emotional dimension (Nafsu Ammarah (Id). In other words, the dark side arises as a result of our inability to manage all of us... The Dark Side appears when we are too focused on shaping our self-image according to the desired ideal, highlighting one part of ourselves and suppressing other parts.
